OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cshot in the face inside a flat
OL,6,FA man was airlifted to hospital after
OL,7,Fbeing shot in the face inside a flat
OL,8,Fin Liverpool.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FHaslingden Close in Old Swan just
OL,12,Fbefore 4.30pm on Monday, January 29.
OL,14,FIt followed a call a man had entered a
OL,15,Fflat and shot another man inside.
OL,17,FThe man was treated by paramedics and
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital via air ambulance
OL,19,Fwith a serious gunshot injury to his
OL,20,Fface.
