OL,6,FMerseyside Police said there were no
OL,7,Ffurther reports of injuries and armed
OL,8,Fpolice remain in the area while an
OL,9,Finvestigation is ongoing to find
OL,10,Fanyone responsible.JDetective Chief
OL,11,FInspector John Fitzgerald said: "The
OL,12,Finvestigation into this shooting is
OL,13,Fstill in the early stages but we
OL,14,Fbelieve it was a targeted attack.
OL,16,F"We are continuing to carry out CCTV
OL,17,Fand house-to-house enquiries to
OL,18,Festablish exactly what happened.
