OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cshot in the face inside a flat
OL,6,F"We are committed to taking weapons
OL,7,Foff our streets to prevent further
OL,8,Fshootings and, rest assured, if you
OL,9,Ftell us where guns are stored and
OL,10,Fbeing used we will take action.J"I
OL,11,Fwould appeal to anyone who was on
OL,12,FHaslingden Close and saw the incident
OL,13,For anything or anyone suspicious to
OL,14,Fcome forward and let us know.
OL,16,F"Similarly, if you have doorbell or
OL,17,Fdashcam footage and live in the area
OL,18,Fthen please review it and tell us if
OL,19,Fyou see anything.
